values: It's been quite a while since my last update.. it seems I only have something to write when things aren't going well... As I venture into my last year of high school, I thought things couldnt be better. Life's been better than it was, but still nothing like NY. I have my share of friends, do my share of partying and just having fun. But like always with my life when things resume to some kind of normal I'm hit down agian. Ryan and Kristie moved back to FL, and I find myself once agian resenting my parents I know it wasnt them who had anything to do with the move, but the fact that hes in my fucking house.. I can't take it.. he's always forgiven for anything and everything he's ever done. I feel like a prisoner in my own house.. before i leave my house I have to think, wheres my wallet, camera, did I leave money around or anything worth money?, ... I'd feel more comfortable letting a stranger in my room, I don't need my shit stolen.. He comes in and without trying turns my life upside down.. and of course no one here understands the things I've been though, I find myself more alone than ever before, I have no one to cry to... no one.. This is my senior year I don't need this shit agian, I can't.. I fucking hate this place called home, take me away, far away.

Nov. 28- work up at 10 to take a shower before work. I had work 11-7, and Shanna was supposed to be moving out while I was at work but she didn't. I love her being here but its so hard to keep my room clean when theres 2x as much laundry and shit. but anyway I'm going to cocoa beach to see Katie tomorrow which is awesome!! except I can't find my bathing suit :(. Shanna said I left it at her place but when she was packing her shit she knows she packed it so I called her up to ask if I can go through her stuff to find it and she said yea, and if I couldn't find it she'd help me look when she got home. So I looked for like 45 min and didn't find it. she came home and looked for 5 min and was like oh well I can't find it I'll buy you a new one and I'm like hey thanks, that's goin to do me a lot of good when I need it for tomorrow.. I mean whatever if she lost it theres nothing I can do about it but the fact that its in her shit and cant spend more than 5 min helping me is bullshit, I tore my room apart to look for it as well and I couldn't find it :(.

Nov. 29- I went to school thinking the whole day how much fun Katie and I were going to have, I miss her so much its so weird not seeing people you saw everyday for 6 months. After school my dad picked me up from school I went home to pack, went to the bank and off to cocoa!! I drove the whole way and no one died! well this one guy did lol I was going like 80mph on this road and a construction worker walks right in front of me, I was like what the fuck are you doing?! lol and I had to pass 3 tolls and almost dropped the quarters cuz there those ones you have to through them in the thing :). When we got there I met Katie's family and then we walked to Ron Jon surf shop and talked a lot about things that have been going on. After we had dinner we went to the beach and got soaked, I haven't been to the beach since I left NY. We called up McD's cuz we both used to work there and we talked to this girl Danielle she's awesome! lol then we called Allie and Suzy at work. After than we went swimming it was so nice to hang out with someone again lol. 

Nov. 30- Katie and I wok up at 8 am and went to Epcot with her family. It was nice cause it wasn't hot out and there weren't tourist everywhere. We went on a few rides and saw a lion king show, we went on test track and I swear it was a whole lot better when I was 10... something about going 60mph isn't so thrilling anymore... we went on some space ride which was really cool at first but after 10-15 sec I was like is it over yet, I got really nauseous. We went to all the countries which was cool, we went on this ride in Spain and the guy running the ride was like " Scotty doesn't know!, Scotty doesn't know" and he was rocking out cause Katie's shirt said "Don't tell Scotty, cause Scotty doesn't know" it was amazingly funny. We saw a bunch of Disney characters so we took pics with beauty and the beast, chip and dale, goofy, and Pluto. Let me know if you want to see the pics I'll send them to you. we also did this thing where you stand there and act all stupid and it plays it back in slow motion so we were doing it for like 10 min and then saw ppl standing there so we thought they wanted to try it so we got out and they were like no we were just watching you, and we were like what?! and there like yea theres a tv right up there, we were just watching you. I don't think we ever laughed so hard. It was an amazing day and a lot better than being in school where I was supposed to be :).. THANKS KATIE FOR AN AMAZING DAY! I LOVE YOU

Nov 23-work 3-10.. long ass day school for 6 hours then work for 7...I had no time to do anything so I git stuck doing my math h/w on break, and had an essay to write when I got home... not a happy camper..

Nov 24- work... what time.. idk??

Nov 25- yup yup, Thanksgiving and guess where I am?? work 8:30am-1pm not a long shift and I get $2 extra an hour so its cool. when I got home I took a nap and when I woke up the family was over :x kill me now. and of course I got stuck cleaning the kitchen.... yea like 75% of it by myself.. but thats the way things go.. and I called a lot of my friends to wish them a happy thanksgiving but it was hard since I have a lot of friends lol. 

Nov 26- worked.. what a surprise.. I dont know why I go home between shift.. I pretty much live there. When I got home Angela called me and she was with Mike and Chris :) I was so happy to talk to them. I miss them soooo much. when I was tlkin to Ang we were talking about "stuff" and shes like "I'm so proud of you!!" and Mike and Chris and like what did she do?!?! and of course the answer was nothing. :). after I got off the phone with them I was talking to Mike Davis <3 lol. we were on the phone for a bit which was cool cuz I havent talked to him in a few weeks. later that night I was talkin to Mike online and he goes so what is Angela so proud of you about? and I said thats best friend kinda stuff aka: classified and he was like whatever. :) "I'll never tell"

Nov 19- I went to school, then took my nap :) I woke up and the family decided we were going to Applebee's for dinner so we got in the car and started driving.... let me tell you about the ass hloe drivers down here.. ok so I'm in the right lane realizing it leads on to I-4 and thats not where I need to be going, I'm goin like 15mph needing to switch into a lane doing 40mph in rush ohur trafic... ok so I find my opening, this guy speeds up rams me back in my lane to swearve to the right of me to get in the lane on the left side of me... make sense?? I think NOT! I went to see Alfi with my older sister Shanna. It was a really good/ cute movie. The movie got out about 12:30am so we went to get somthing to eat and made fun of the fat waitress :) and the guy siting behind us who was...interesting Nov 20- work 9:30-5 and its JILLIAN MIGLIARG'S BIRTHDAY! Nov 21- I called Freda cuz it's her birfday, we gonna party like it's her birfday I miss my Freda :( Nov 22- work 3:30-8:30

Nov. 13- I went to work and thought it was going to be the worst day ever, it just that kinda feel to the air.. and it was a bad or till break, I got to relax and just chill. I went back to work and I met this guy Joe who ironically enough works with my sisters x-b/f JR. So he gave me his number and asked to hang out and I said I'd give him a call. I called JR and he said that Joe reminded him of Ryan.. so I was like fuck that then. later that day I met this id Joey him and his mom came through the line and the computer got fucked up so we were waiting for it to reboot and got to talking something happened to Joey when he was younger and now he's somewhat retarded but he asked me and this girl Lauren for out numbers so we gave it to him. He seemed nice and if it would make him happy to talk than I'd be happy to help. :) 

Nov. 14- FUCK THIS TOWN I GOT MY TICKETS TO NY TODAY... 42 DAYS!!! 

Nov 15- Took a math test Friday.... got a 51% on it :( not so happy... on the bright side its one of the highest math grades I got this year! worked 5:30-10:30. and Britt told me her mom said I can stay with them for a night when I come to NY :)!!

Nov 16-???

Nov. 17- progress report! English A, DCT A, Marine Sci C, American History A, Math F..

On Friday I went to school and it was a normal day till I was walking to American History... there was a fight, like 2-3 girls... black girls.. ripping each others weave out and ppl are pickin it up and waving it in the air. and one girl got her shirt ripped off, it was like something you'd see in CI.... so totally never in Hauppauge! but after school I had to work 3-9:30 which sucked because I haven't really seen my dad in days because he's been sleeping when I come home from work, and now he's in Miami for the weekend cause the Jests are playing. 

Sat- I had work 9:30-5:30... what a waste of my day! I was text messaging my friend Sean all through work cuz he works down the road from me and he said he was bored so when I got off I got him some food and brought it to him.. he was grateful cause he wasn't feeling good and all but I'm glad I cheered him up! I went home and had dinner then we were all sooo bored so Shanna, JR, Devin, our cousin Alyssa and I went to Daytona. It took like an hour to get there and we stayed for like 45 min just walking around the bored walk but it was good, something to do. and that was my Saturday.

Sunday I had to work... what a surprise 8:30-3:30. This girl Lauren and I did returns for like 35 min it was kinda cool, and easy. We had this cunt of a customer she comes in all bitchy an saying shity like Oh could you get me such and such cigs or is that to hard? and demanding all this shit I was like who the fuck does she think she is? but whatever I blew it off. After work Robin and Ben were over so we went looking at Halloween stuff it was kinda cool... And Angela moved home today!

Nothing really went on this week. On Wednesday I was sitting in math class and this kid Ali started passing me notes that said:
 Ali-"You didn't call me last night"
  Me-"I went to sleep early and I had an essay to write for english.. whats with wanting me to call you so bad?"
  Ali- "I thought we were gonna f*ck"
  Me- "What gave you that idea?"
  Ali- "cuz you said we were gonna, do you want to or not"
  Me (I remember telling him that.. but kidding around..)"no offence but you seem like the type whos been around, so no thanx"
 So through the week he'd badger me about differnt things, like asking what I was doing after school cuz he wanted me to give him head... and asked me what I was doing this weekedn and I said idk why and he goes "cuz I wana smoke (weed) and fuck you" So I said good luck with that. so when I said no he said why not? I'll eat you out so yes or maybe? so I said or no... and he writes F*CK YOU really big on the note.......so thats how that went..

Friday I went to work, then went to the movie with my cousin Kay, we saw Vanity fair.. It was alright, but not my cup of tea.. we got back to her house at like 12:30 and I had to get up at like 9:30 cuz I had work in the am :( but it was good, a night out..and today I didn't do much cuz I was at work but we were really busy cuz theres another hunnicane coming! this is getting old.. There are no hurricanes in NY!! no fair!

Today Ang and I woke up about 11 and went in the pool. We got some hott tan lines let me tell you! :). but of course I had work at 3. So I sent Ryan, Devin, Angela, and Jillian to the movies so when it was over we could meet for lunch while I was on break. Then I went back to work and did carts most of the night with Angie (not Angela)we got to talk and get to know each other a little better so it was cool. Angela called me and few hours later all upset about Mike (her x, not Hayes) so being the awesome friend I am I brought here home some ice cream! We talked for a little bit but it was just one of those moods where you hate boys and you just need to sleep on it and wake up alllll better. So she went to sleep about 1am, I was up till 5am on the phone w/ Eddie. We talked about all kinds of stuff. 

    Today Angela and I were supposed to go to the mall with Janelle and Angie today but it didn't work out, so we watched secret window instead, of course I fell asleep but the afternoon was good, we had the house to our selves and we got to talk like we used to. Eddie came over about 8:30 I guess. We watched the VMA's till 10 and he had to go b/c I had h/w to do. He was kinda being an ass when I told him he had to go. but that what Angela is for. She told him off :)

Yesterday when my mom picked my up from school my cousin Rob was with her and I was like krjgneugbne. I don't like him, I'm sure most of you have heard me talk of him. He's my cousin with all the drug issues and 3 kids. It's really sad being like 30+ no job, no car, no home. He lives with his mommy how fucked up. Anyway I had to go to the mall because my moms birthday was tomorrow. But we had to wait for my brother Ken to come over and baby-sit my cousin. My dad told him don't take your eyes off of him. Its really sad that you can't trust a grown man in your house. So anyway my dad, Jackie and I went to the mall but no luck I hate shopping for my mom. I put thought into stuff and I love gadget type stuff like from Brookstone but she likes things to put in the china closet and I hate that kinda stuff I think its a useless gift and I refuse to buy her something like that. which makes it hard... anyway we went back home. and a little bit later Jackie and I had to drive Rob back to my aunts house. I didn't want to go over there because for a lack of better words they're white trash I hate going over there its such a dysfunctional house. So we were there for like 45 min then we went back to the mall to shop for my mom.. Then to Starbucks. It was an average day I suppose.

     Tuesday-- Today I went to school and it was a normal gay ass day at Lake Mary High till 2nd period anyway, this kid I liked back in the 6th grade asked my for my number.. I was sooo happy the rest of the day you have no idea. His name is Lloyd and he's sooo hott. anyway today was also my moms birthday EVEYONE in the family came over + some. There were like 25 people here... I thought to my self there are 25 to many people here lol. The family hung out I did the usual hibernating in my room thing. I went out to sing happy birthday do my mommy ;) then Devin decided to wipe icing on me. I scooped an entire handful of icing off the top of the cake and wiped it in her hair and ears. It was hott! lol she got all mad at me but I was like whatever you started it. And it is also Jessica Ferrara's B-day so I called her, it was good to talk to her again.

Well today was the thrid day of school.. I hate it. I have no one to talk to and its so frustrating to not have anyone to talk to. In Hauppauge even if I didn't have a close friend in the class there was always someone there to talk to. In American history we had to write an essay and we had 3 different choices so me being the slacker I am I sat there and wrote Angela a letter. I felt a tap on my back and I thought it the kid behind me just moved a book and it hit me, but then I felt it again and I turned around and he wrote me a note saying:
Hey Cassandra whats up. nuttin here just really bored and writting this stupid fuckin essay how was your day today? mine was boring [then he contuined about some stuid shit I ddint understand] Which question are you doing? I am doing the American citizen bullshit one. But anyways I wana know if you wana hook up cause your pretty hott but no b/f g/f thing cuz we barely know eachother.
                                 Rick
OMG idk but it was the funniest thing ever. I was trying not to laugh, it was soo random.
 So after my gay ass day at school yesterday Shanna and JR came over to take me out to eat becasue i didn't like what the family was ahving for dinner, we went out and my dad called us and said he had to go out because something happend with my cousin that may or may not involve the police. This is my cousin Rob whos into all the drugs and shit and has the three kids he doesnt take care of/ support. He's almost 40 and lives at home its really sad how much of a fuck up he is. He is looking at a lot of jail time right now. and his kids don't respect him or even like him. I could imagine the betrail they must feel. All they did was being born they don't deserve this fuck up for a "father". But anyway I got home and the rents were still out so Shanna JR and I just chilled I really like that I have them here. It's an escape and they know exactly how I feel with this family bullshit all the time becasue they did it as well but thinmgs were better back then, I guess because we were all young naive. Anyway today after school I went to the DMV to change my permit to a FL one, I wanted to keep my NY one but they don't let you, then I went to Albersons for an interview but the manager was busy so I have to go back Firday.

Hey kids I'm in french with the coolest freshmen ever- Crystal, Kylee, and Christina. Were supposed to be writing an eight paragraph essay in French but it was an accumulation of shit we did over the year life homework and shit which as most of you kno I don't really do h/w to often.... We're also taking our speaking test today which is part of our final. I got a 9 out of 20 last year so I'm hoping for a 10 this year :). Doesn't take much to make me happy. Other than French nothin is really going on. I started work last week I think and I really like it there it's making me no want to move even more. I was talking to Jimmy earlier today about it and I started crying :'( I'll be ok though I mean theres nothing I can do to stop it so I guess I'll make the best of it. But yea all the people at work are super cool. I hope people don't forget about me and I become one of those "what ever happened to her" type people cuz I want to keep in touch with everyone but it's hard. And it's goin to be weird when I move b/c I'm goin to the same school with the same ppl I did 4 years ago but I didn't keep in touch with anyone so Idk what everyone is like now and I know I'm not the same person I was then. I do have my older sister there though which is cool she's 21 so we can chill a lot and I'll hopefully get my car this summer. But who knows. To anyone thats reading this keep in touch I'll try to update my journal more often so you can at least know whats going on with me. I Love You all so much. xoxo.

Well todays a pretty boring day nothing excited happened, I was supposed to have a earth Science test today but we didnt finish the lab yesterday so when we got there he posponded the test to Monday which is good and bad because now I have 5 tests on Monday.... :(. But we went through lab folders instead and I realized I'm missing 3 labs and I know I did them but there missing so I called my mom and asked her to look in my binder in my room and there missing which sux cuz progress reports are next week so I have to do them all but now I'm in English and I have nothing to do cuz I didi all my work I guess you could say I couyld study but this is me we are talking bout.... Tonight should be fub Mike didin't have his car most of the week and he got it back last night so were going out to th movies tonight but who knows anyway the bell is going to ring son so I have to go.

I hate 4/20 to all of my so called friends I understand you like to smoke pot whether it be everyday or once a month. But knowing I hate the idea of drugs all together I would appreciate it if you would have the decency not to be like OMG I smoked and.... Thats a part of your life I don't want to know anything about. I've been so overwhelmed with it b/c it was 4/20 the other day and it's quite annoying. I understand you may think I'm being critical or unreasonable and I'm perfectly fine with that. But I need all of you to understand I don't want to have any part in it or knowing about or I will have no other choice than to discontinue our friendship b/c I'm not jeopardizing my morals for your "good time." If I have to choose between your stories or my feelings sorry but I chose me.

I went to school Wed. all tired as usual thinking the day would completely suck but then I remembered I have Boces to go to. If was really cool. I want to do cosmetology but I'm like the whitest person there but I still think it would be really cool. I also checked out culinary arts. It was cool but I like the girly stuff better you know hair, nail and things of that sort. When I got back I found out with the curve for the regents I got a 76 I was happy and annoyed at the same time cuz I got a 18 point curve which was cool. But I didn't work for it. I don't like being handed grades and I'm not used to good grades lately. But whatever it looks good to schools I guess. The rest of school was just a normal day. I had plans after school to hang out with Mike, we went to his house and didn't watch finding Nemo if you get what I'm saying lol. His dad came in when we were being good and said what are you guys watching? Cartoons? and I said no were watching finding Nemo and he goes if that like finding Waldo? hahaha it was soooo funny it's an inside joke but I kno some of you will get it so I thought I'd share. He drove me home around 5 and no surprise ended up fighting with my parents for lord knows what reason. But it happens. Today we also decided to hang out and well things got even more physical. ;) lol. I like being close to him both physically and mentally. He's like the only joy in my day/life.

Well the past few days have consisted of nothing but fighting in my house. It's terrible. I avoid home as much as I can because it's all a bunch of bullshit. Ryan's no longer moving out, So the hope of getting my family back is gone. And my parents think I'm the one with something wrong. I'm always wrong, so there sending me to see the school social worker.. I forget her name. What she says makes sense but the way she tells me to do things isn't me and with that aside I have tried what she tells me but nothing seems to help. I tell my parents how much I hate being home because every night I find my self crying, longing for someone to call at 1am. All my grades have gone down, I'm extra tired from the crying, and I'm not happy at home. But the funny thing is it's only when Ryan's around but my parents are in complete denial of everything. Because e I'm the out spoken out and don't sit there and let him be a dick to me I'm wrong. You would think I could win once.

Today I woke up for breakfast and b/c it's a Sunday I eat with the family but my dad was in Fl. and unfortunaty Ryan was with us to eat. We didn't fight through breakfast, but after breakfast he stared fighting with my mom and yelling at her like he always does. so I got pissed and intervened and he got pissed at me and goes why don't you tell mom how you were hanging out with Mike last night instead of bowling like you said. And my mom looked at my all pissed an I said I didn't lie to you I did go bowling I just left Mike out of the plans. I thought she was goin to be annoyed but it was ok. At least now they know.

Tonight was soo much fun! Allie came over about 7 and we went to Commack bowling Ally where we met up with Mike. We bowled 2 games and I did sooo bad the first game and kicked ass the second. But we had bumpers too lol. It was all good. In the first game Mike was beating me and Allie so when it was his turn we screamed sexual things to distract him. It worked sometimes but other times he'd get a strike or something good like that. After our games we went to get our shoes at the desk and we stood there for ever and a fucking day I was getting really annoyed I was like I just want my fucking shoe. We decided we wanted pizza so I drove to the pizza place which was in the next parking lot but I did a good job and parked straight. :) YaY. But there was this car that came out of no where... and it almost hit us but it didn't... and it was my right of way anyway so it's all good. When we were eating I called him cell from a blocked number about 10 times and he didn't catch on the it was me. lol He still doesn't know. :) I'm a funny kid. It was then 10:15 and we didn't know what to do cuz I didn't have to be home till 11:30 so we went and played pool... Well me and Allie did. We made fools of ourselves but what else is new... Turns out we can't play pool. We went to 7-11 after that and happened to run into my brother, He seemed like something was bothering him and as much as I hate him I went over and asked if he was ok and he said yes, I asked him not to tell my mom I was with Mike and he said ok. Then since we were in CI it's not uncommon but I was literally in the middle of a drug deal. A car was on one side of us and a guy parked on the other side and got out to pick up his shit.... I felt violated :(. So yea that was my night... Much fun

Tonight was mucho fun. I was kinda tired from last nights party but this one was sooo much fun, more of the people I was friends with were there. We once again danced allll night. Megan looked amazing. Her dress was strapless and baby blue with beads all over the top half then flared out at the bottom. she looked amazing. We all tried to get her to dance with her boyfriend but they weren't to into it. I guess she's one of those held back people when it comes to her and her boyfriend being around the family. I got to catch up with some of my friends that I don't get to see as much anymore because of other crowds of friends, lack of time and no classes together. When I got home I ached sooo much. I went straight to bed.
